<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='361409' id='t-361409'>We quickly came to a decision in those 10 minutes.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='364822' id='t-364822'>This time it was not the military,</span>
