</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='462478' id='t-462478'>Greece, you see, was only a preview</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='464933' id='t-464933'>of what is in store for us all.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467310' id='t-467310'>I, overly optimistically, had hoped</span>
