<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='555823' id='t-555823'>But let me warn you, this is not just about Greece.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='559135' id='t-559135'>This could be the pattern</span>
