<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='694759' id='t-694759'>So let's try something else.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='696347' id='t-696347'>Let's see how we can bring people back to the process.</span>
